          <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin: 0.5rem 0;">Tech Startups Thrive in Counties</h2>
        </a>
        <p style="line-height: 1.6;">Local tech startups report record funding, signaling a shift in the economic landscape.</p>
        <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #666;">April 04, 2025</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Add more articles as needed -->
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>